continue the weapons drain 
a military solution cannot work not only because neither side 
can defeat the other but more fundamentally because there are 
not two sides a victory of any of the many contending forces 
would provoke a civil war on the part of those who are excluded 
he said 
he said the goal should be a political settlement in which the 
