joffrey ballet in no way affects the joffrey ballet school 
director edith daddario said the school is an independent 
organization and mr arpino is still and will remain the artistic 
director of the joffrey ballet school 
arpino who became artistic director of the ballet company in 
1988 after the death of founder robert joffrey resigned tuesday 
after the joffrey board of directors voted to set up an operating 
committee that would run the company in place of both arpino and 
the 55member board 
ten board members resigned in protest at what one called a 
takeover by businessmen ignorant of artistic matters 
arpino has been a dancer and choreographer with the modern 
ballet company since its early days in the mid1950s however 
critics and dance buffs alike have often called his works 
pedestrian instead of inspired and without structure purpose or 
artistry with the exception of such works as sea shadow 1962 
and viva vivaldi 1965 arpino is considered a secondrate 
choreographer who merely moves dancers around a stage 
