through a jungle 
i see and feel that latvia wont retreat from the principle of 
independence landsbergis said in separate remarks to latvian 
radio 
pro and antiindependence protesters surrounded the latvian 
deputies as they entered the parliament building 
about 50 soviet army officers who live in latvia gathered with 
