the explosion in the cocaine trafficking center was the latest 
involving the la rebaja pharmacy chain police have blamed previous 
attacks on the continuing war between the rival medellin and cali 
cocaine cartels 
the bomb went off in the crowded alameda neighborood destroying 
the la rebaja pharmacy and smashing windows and causing other 
damage in 13 nearby businesses col jaime sierra director of the 
police in cali told the network 
