the joint venture will develop manufacture and market jet 
engines of up to 20000 pounds of thrust which power small 
civilian and military jets capable of carrying up to about 100 
passengers 
the venture called bmwrollsroyce will collaborate with 
rollsroyces own tay and trent jet engine programs the british 
company said in a separate press statement but it said it would 
not merge any of its existing engine operations into the venture 
bmwrollsroyce will then commence the design and development 
of new engines of less than 20000 pounds of thrust to meet 
