its position in the aircraft engine industry 
ive always looked at rollsroyce as kind of the weak 
thirdparty player he said 
general electric co and the pratt amp whitney division of united 
technologies corp each hold 40 percent to 45 percent of the 
worldwide engine market while rollsroyce has a 15 percent to 20 
percent share he said 
the new venture will be geared up for strong growth over the 
next five to 10 years bmw officials said declining to project 
sales targets 
