venture could aim for as much as the equivalent of 595 million in 
yearly sales within the next decade 
to reach that goal however the two parent companies probably 
would have to invest as much as 1 billion marks or about 595 
million in expansion the experts added 
bmw built aircraft engines through world war ii and by the end 
of the war it produced turbines for the newly developed jet 
airplane 
