able to trade ahead of major market trends and the firms customers 
the practice of trading with advance knowledge of incoming 
customer orders is known as front running it is illegal in the 
securities and commodity futures markets but frontrunning between 
the markets is unregulated because neither the sec nor the cftc has 
authority over the others markets 
he said that aside from the information exchanges by what he 
